('https://cdorgs.github.io/', 'About', '', 'build, organism, organisms, normal, frog, ai, biological, cells, living, design', 'How they’re madePress releasehttps://www.uvm.edu/uvmnews/news/team-builds-first-living-robotsFAQWhat is the big picture here — is it just about robots made of frog cells?\nWe made these out of normal frog cells, with a normal frog genome.\nFrog cells were pieced together to form a new configuration, which is different from a frog.\nHowever, living organisms (those made by human-guided mating, bacteria and viruses generated by human travel and impact on the foodchain, etc.)\nIf an AI did indeed design these organisms, couldn’t an evil (or ignorant) AI design harmful (or unintentionally harmful) organisms?', '2021-12-03', 'https://cdorgs.github.io/img/icon.png', 'cdorgs.github.io'),
